==Text==
Dear Little Gray:

<div align="center">Originally, Tribbie was supposed to write this letter.<br />
But Trianne also has a lot to say to you!<br />
In the end, '''we''' decided to write one line each...

'''We''' once delivered prophecies to city-states scattered far and wide.<br />
'''We''' once opened gateways for the Chrysos Heirs warring across the lands!<br />
'''We''' once listened to prophecies in the Temple of Janus...

In the end, Little Gray fulfilled '''our''' Flame-Chase wish.<br />
Little Gray drove away the villains emerging from the black tide!<br />
It was Little Gray who saved everyone in Amphoreus...

So, please accept this Tribbie plushie,<br />
Trianne stuffed the cotton inside, she worked so hard!<br />
And Trinnon sewed it together, stitch by stitch...

The three of '''us''' have written enough already. Next, here's a wish from a thousand of '''us''':<br />
May you ride the west wind to where the flowers bloom. There is no need to be saddened by partings.<br />
We'll see you tomorrow!

Tribios</div>

